# Navigation Flow

The app uses Expo Router for navigation with the following structure:

## Main Screens

- [app/(tabs)/index.tsx](mdc:app/(tabs)/index.tsx) - Home/Dashboard
- [app/(tabs)/library.tsx](mdc:app/(tabs)/library.tsx) - Course Library
- [app/(tabs)/achievements.tsx](mdc:app/(tabs)/achievements.tsx) - User achievements
- [app/(tabs)/profile.tsx](mdc:app/(tabs)/profile.tsx) - User profile

## Auth Flow

- [app/(auth)/onboarding.tsx](mdc:app/(auth)/onboarding.tsx) - Onboarding screen
- [app/(auth)/sign-in.tsx](mdc:app/(auth)/sign-in.tsx) - Login screen
- [app/(auth)/sign-up.tsx](mdc:app/(auth)/sign-up.tsx) - Registration screen

## Content Screens

- [app/chapter/[chapterId].tsx](mdc:app/chapter/[chapterId].tsx) - Chapter content view
- [app/lesson/[lessonId].tsx](mdc:app/lesson/[lessonId].tsx) - Lesson details view
